e:0pt;width:100%;margin:0 auto\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"vertical-align:top\">\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;font-weight:20px\"><span style=\"color:#87189d\"><strong>​</strong></span></p>\r\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;text-align:center;table-layout:fixed;float:none\" class=\"email-image\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"vertical-align:top\"><figure style=\"margin:1em 0;margin-top:12px;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;max-width:200px;width:100%\"><div style=\"display:block\"><img src=\"https://embed.filekitcdn.com/e/w9w6tnaQKj8JcctQR6fbCh/7MBuzxzU9HzvjjAdcPobD\" alt=\"Innovating with AI\" width=\"200\" height=\"auto\" style=\"border:0 none;display:block;height:auto;line-height:100%;outline:none;-webkit-text-decoration:none;text-decoration:none;max-width:100%;max-width:100% !important;border-radius:4px 4px 4px 4px;width:200px;height:auto;object-fit:contain\"></div></figure></td></tr></tbody></table>\r\n</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>\r\n<div class=\"email-body\" style=\"margin-bottom:20px;overflow:hidden;padding:50px 35px;background-color:#ffffff\"><div class=\"email-content\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;width:100%;margin:0 auto\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"vertical-align:top\">\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">Hey Will,</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">Enrollment for the <strong>AI Consultancy Project</strong> – our program for you to <strong>engineer ROI with AI </strong>using our PROOF Process™ for consultants and owner-operators – closes tonight at <strong>11:59 PM Pacific</strong>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">This is the last email I’ll send about joining the program for this cohort. If you know the timing isn’t right for you, that’s okay – IWAI will be here when you’re ready.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">If something else is giving you a bit of pause, then I want you to know you're not alone…</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:1em;margin:0;font-size:1.5em;margin:1em 0;font-weight:normal;font-family:Georgia,Times,'Times New Roman',serif;color:#222222;line-height:1.2\"><strong>Story Time: Me, 14 years ago in Washington, DC...</strong></h2>\r\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;text-align:center;table-layout:fixed;float:none\" class=\"email-image\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"vertical-align:top\"><figure style=\"margin:1em 0;margin-top:12px;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;max-width:240px;width:100%\"><div style=\"display:block\"><img src=\"https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXfyO9YBGD2Civ1X6tVrVhyt3PgEL5dZVKw3GMSdbhjI7k0acH99ubdnOM25Ad4GaXwMcBnTf_s_9FdFp9t7x1N6VlDPI4P4CKaMUAJx8m3-X4YpUWPNYBdvNqB4iP_8vk8hnTAMOQ?key=Zqy6GITvkotsMJTuFZ0x4Th5\" alt=\"Me and my wife in DC in 2010\" width=\"240\" height=\"auto\" style=\"border:0 none;display:block;height:auto;line-height:100%;outline:none;-webkit-text-decoration:none;text-decoration:none;max-width:100%;max-width:100% !important;border-radius:4px 4px 4px 4px;width:240px;height:auto;object-fit:contain\"></div></figure></td></tr></tbody></table>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">The Rob you’re looking at there was making $50K per year as a solo developer and lovestruck for the woman sitting next to him. They didn’t have much - just a 1-bedroom apartment between the two of them and a daily routine.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">She’d go off to work at a DC accounting firm.<br>He’d work remotely from the kitchen countertop.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">It wasn’t much, and yet, I felt like I had it all. I knew she was the one for me, and I was determined to create a life we’d always be grateful for.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">As for what that looked like…well, if anything, I had a much better idea of what I didn’t want:</p>\r\n<div style=\"font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;padding:10px 20px;margin:0 0 20px;border-left-style:solid;border-left-width:5px;border-left-color:#e1e1e1\" class=\"blockquotes\">\r\n<div class=\"blockquotes-line\">❌ 60-80+ hour work weeks that kept us apart.<br>​</div>\r\n<div class=\"blockquotes-line\">❌ Saying no to vacations because I had to \"put in extra weekend work.\"<br>​</div>\r\n<div class=\"blockquotes-line\">❌ To become an “absent” dad and partner who, even when in the room, was “away in his head at work.”<br>​</div>\r\n<div class=\"blockquotes-line\">❌ Having zero time or energy to give back to the causes we cared about.<br>​</div>\r\n<div class=\"blockquotes-line\">❌ Scraping by to make ends meet, constantly stressed about what came next.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">I was willing to do whatever it took to not end up like this.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">I wanted more.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">And after over a decade of ‘figuring it out’, I can say this… </p>\r\n<h2 class=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:1em;margin:0;font-size:1.5em;margin:1em 0;font-weight:normal;font-family:Georgia,Times,'Times New Roman',serif;color:#222222;line-height:1.2\">\r\n<strong>Now: I have more time to date my wife </strong>(and hang with our son)</h2>\r\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;mso-table-lspace:0pt;mso-table-rspace:0pt;text-align:center;table-layout:fixed;float:none\" class=\"email-image\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"vertical-align:top\"><figure style=\"margin:1em 0;margin-top:12px;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;max-width:232px;width:100%\"><div style=\"display:block\"><img src=\"https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXeP5Pso5n5S6JGSbp4aPn6VStcNAL5E9sAK27MdLcLLp-yALUwBLmcayt3jCQJV3txC1migoiNqh8QzxW0fAg3em3g--1-r5sP1eNAcfxDd5gyn0Iq6R-5CIWUQqyX6EeYaqUwtGw?key=Zqy6GITvkotsMJTuFZ0x4Th5\" alt=\"Back in DC with our son 10 years later!\" width=\"232\" height=\"auto\" style=\"border:0 none;display:block;height:auto;line-height:100%;outline:none;-webkit-text-decoration:none;text-decoration:none;max-width:100%;max-width:100% !important;border-radius:4px 4px 4px 4px;width:232px;height:auto;object-fit:contain\"></div></figure></td></tr></tbody></table>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">Fast forward to today and life looks very different.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">My smile is even wider than the first pic because hey, the love of my life became my wife, and we have a son who knows he’s loved by both his parents.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">That dream life we envisioned in our first apartment?</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\"> After years of choosing ‘the path less traveled’, it became a reality: I built a $2M/year <s>service</s> freedom business.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">One that allows me to do things like:</p>\r\n<ul class=\"unordered_list\" style=\"margin:1em 0;margin-left:1em;padding:0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;list-style-position:outside !important\">\r\n<li class=\"list_item\" style=\"padding:0 0 0 1em;margin:0;margin-left:1em\"><span>Date my wife all over again at our old date spots</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"list_item\" style=\"padding:0 0 0 1em;margin:0;margin-left:1em\"><span>Take father-son trips to hangout with Pokémon in Japan</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"list_item\" style=\"padding:0 0 0 1em;margin:0;margin-left:1em\"><span>\"Bucket-list family trips\" to places like Antarctica</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">I’m talking about the kind of freedom where I take my wife to revisit all our old date spots, while taking my son to tour the Smithsonian museums, and capping it all off with a family beach trip to Delaware.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">Great times… and whenever I got back to my home office, there is NO mountain pile-up of work – my systems and team take care of it.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">Email?</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">Done in less than 1 hour.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">Instead of feeling chained to the chair on a Monday, I'm thankful for everything that got done while I was away.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">Life is <em>very</em> different now.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">Back then, I made $50K a year and was $20,000 in credit-card debt.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">Then, just 1 year later, I made $175K – that 3.5X jump happened because I decided to stop ‘fucking around with freelancing’ and finally get serious.<br>​<br>(btw, all the client and consultancy skills + systems I built back then are all part of the Trusted Advisor Skills Engine™ - 14 years later, they’re still relevant, even with AI).</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">It's interesting… because I’ve had friends who were paid just as well, even more so, but they rarely had all 4 freedoms... </p>\r\n<ul class=\"unordered_list\" style=\"margin:1em 0;margin-left:1em;padding:0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;list-style-position:outside !important\">\r\n<li class=\"list_item\" style=\"padding:0 0 0 1em;margin:0;margin-left:1em\"><span><strong>Freedom of Time:</strong> Spend your days on things that matter—whether that’s work, family, or exploring something new.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"list_item\" style=\"padding:0 0 0 1em;margin:0;margin-left:1em\"><span><strong>Freedom of Money:</strong> Build stability for yourself and your loved ones while enjoying the life you’ve worked for.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"list_item\" style=\"padding:0 0 0 1em;margin:0;margin-left:1em\"><span><strong>Freedom of Relationships:</strong> Surround yourself with people who uplift you and align with your values.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"list_item\" style=\"padding:0 0 0 1em;margin:0;margin-left:1em\"><span><strong>Freedom of Purpose:</strong> Live a life that’s meaningful to you, whether through your work, loved ones, or giving back.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">Now, after having done it, and repeatedly showing others to do it, I can confidently say I’ve found a timeless way to do it.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">Investing in yourself.<br>Finding the right mentor.<br>Committing to your goals.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">To create lasting change in life, these things have always been true. Do it right, and a life of flexible freedom isn't some pie-in-the-sky dream. It's doable so long as you're willing to put in the work.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">What's different now is <strong>The AI Economy </strong>– there’s even more opportunity…and also more risk for anyone without a clear way to engineer ROI with AI.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;color:#404040;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5\">Sure, it'll still take work, but you’re no stranger to hard work. The difference with this, is every hour of work you put into this is a step closer to more of the life you want.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" style=\"margin:1em 0;font-size:18px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:-appl